data.description: This 3 bed 2 bath home ranch is full potential equity and updates including landscaping, underground sprinklers, siding, roof, gutters, garage door, water heater, all new privacy fence as well as new countertops and tile shower in the main floor bathroom! The basement has been partially finished and is ready for its new owner to finish the final touches.   Framing, plumbing and electrical were all completed in 2022. It is partially drywalled as well.  When finished, there would be 4th legal bedroom, a third full bathroom and a family room to relax in.  Come enjoy small town living at its best in Hickman!
